Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:20.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:22.93,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.14,0:00:29.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:40.45,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:43.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.12,0:00:49.25,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.63,0:00:55.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.84,0:01:02.60,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.89,0:01:07.06,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.14,0:01:09.31,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:16.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.49,0:01:26.66,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.83,0:01:30.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.33,0:01:35.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:41.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, let's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:48.94,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:53.19,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:55.53,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:59.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.03,0:02:02.45,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:04.66,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.74,0:02:06.20,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:07.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:09.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:11.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:13.04,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:14.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:15.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:19.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:22.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.09,0:02:26.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.47,0:02:28.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:32.77,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.98,0:02:35.19,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:39.57,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:42.28,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything \Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:02:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything this \Nworld has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the \NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the Straw Hat Pirates\N headed for the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a suspicious ship appeared before them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew helped\N those aboard the ship, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is someone else I'd like you to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that the patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Click.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have managed to successfully\N drive the prey into a tight corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How appropriate for such a splendid day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you call this a "mission"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.28,0:03:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Count us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to steal this ship \Nand prepare to strike back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As things stand now, Vigaro-san \Nwill never be able to rest in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, punks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're free toargue amongst yourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I don't like the direction \Nthis conversation's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sunny's in a Pinch! \NRoar, Secret Super-Speed Mecha"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get worked up, brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for the record, we aren't \Nthe least bit suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're really just a group\N of good-natured fishermen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.18,0:04:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, men?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll only let your sketchy antics go so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simple fishermen don't offer pirates \Nbooze laced with some anesthetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, it's time you came clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.43,0:05:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we have a heart-to-heart, I think\N we can and can't see eye-to-eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with them, Guile!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only three of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take this ship by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can go back to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm through with taking \Norders from those freaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But they've been so good to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just too heartless!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you won't seize their ship, we will!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, don't hurt the lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't hurt her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.27,0:05:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's your answer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice and straightforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A few of mycrew mates have short fuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like they meant you any harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "eheh heh" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to hide?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They clearly "meant us harm"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brrr!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.03,0:06:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't dealt with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought they seemed fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For fishermen, you didn't seem like \Nyouwere all that great at fishing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't naïve enough to fall for that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minus a certain two, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Commander Stansen...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, you'd better be ready to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, we'll just have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna give your whole crew a watery grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave them be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, have you seen Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find him anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crud!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gettinga bad feeling about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those men must have kidnapped him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That seems likely enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch, the punks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, the quickest way to find \Nout is to board their ship and ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind is picking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This could turn into a storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that having been said,what \Nshould we do about these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's super cold out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my head hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to underestimate them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've ruined the plan I devised!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm terribly sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Next time, we'll--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can pull back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said that I want you worthless \Npieces of trash to keep out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I make myself clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.49,0:08:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.41,0:08:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.07,0:08:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Click.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men, we have a change of plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going with Trap: Sea Gull.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn those jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare they trick us like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.43,0:09:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you hiding Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Straw Hat, I hate to do this \Nafter you took such good care of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's time we parted ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.02,0:09:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec, geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to cut the rope\N that's connecting our ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind--!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A power holder?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your powers won't help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.21,0:10:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's another Devil Fruit power holder?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Salchow-sama, Trap: Sea Gull is set!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's get it under way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's show time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that music?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming from over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the music?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's the Marines!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've already sniffed us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd they have to show up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.79,0:10:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get us out of here, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats' ship is on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we give them a bit of a scare?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're firing at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry it up, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna blow us sky-high!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.36,0:11:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light up, pronto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in front of us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard left rudder!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dance, dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light up Numbers Six, Seven, and Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.99,0:11:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.63,0:11:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're over here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.66,0:11:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.23,0:12:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be real!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.18,0:12:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Nami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please figure somethin' out, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you're annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to think!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san, there is a hole \Nright through there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.90,0:12:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.65,0:12:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?! Where?! Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There really is one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think we can make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind changed directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get on course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.39,0:12:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take any more of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rudder won't budge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:12:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.27,0:13:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a Soldier Dock \NSystem for times like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Channel 0...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With its cola-run engine,\N it's the Paddle Ship Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jiro, lend me a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This rocking is going to \Nsplit his wounds back open!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo! We got through!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the Marines can't \Ndo a thing to stop us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.19,0:13:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can keep up with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The operation is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We successfully got the Straw \NHatsto head for the Arctic Path.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They fell for it hook, line, and sinker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a great success!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have no hope to escape now, none at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's report to Campaccino-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.53,0:14:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came to get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me know if you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.81,0:14:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dr. Chopper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take another--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:14:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, knock that off...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you kowtowing to him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.89,0:15:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am terribly sorry about \Nhow rude we've been!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad about tricking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.75,0:15:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.65,0:15:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just cameto get Chopper back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy keeps throwing me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go searchfor your \Nship's doctor right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were here after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry on back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take off with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still need the doctor to stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're dead set on \Ntaking him now, I'll...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Jiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if he does?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not afraid to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not like you cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:15:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care how strong he is, \NI'm never gonna lose ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, what the heck is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.44,0:16:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,honestly, I want to stay \Nhere for a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a patient who is badly hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already finished the operation, \Nbut he's still in critical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to look after him until \Nhe regains consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.41,0:16:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, we can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, thank you for \Nwhat you said back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jiro, I don't know much about you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks like you can't \Ndisclose what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may be a pirate, but I'm also a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I see someone in pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it doesn't matter who he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.18,0:16:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd give my life to treat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're also a band of pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.89,0:17:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this man is the captain of \Nour pirate band, the Phoenix Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Puzzle-san the Phoenix.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phoenix...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how dangerous the situation got,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.04,0:17:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter how severely he got injured,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.38,0:17:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he always stood back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was just like a phoenix...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I burnt him to a crisp!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't feel a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't kill me with that toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me and the guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all felt that he was going \Nto become the King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But things were different over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World was on \Na completely different level.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went to the New World?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:17:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we didn't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't even take Puzzle-san seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.42,0:18:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to escape somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They truly were on a completely \Ndifferent level...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still believe that Puzzle-san will \Nrise back up, just like a phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse that jerk Stansen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit leaving "Commander" out \Nwhen you say his name!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll whack us again if he hears you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just abouthad it with \Nthat freaking coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.03,0:18:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel the same way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guile's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.28,0:18:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you stand things the way they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long must we endure this humiliation?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.84,0:18:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First they stole our Jolly Roger,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then they made us their lackeys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.02,0:19:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather die than join the likes of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think Vigaro was willing to \Nsacrifice his life to protect yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare throw your life away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.98,0:19:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We believe that once the \Ncaptain has recovered,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll steal our Jolly Roger back and \Nreturn to our pirate ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I bet Stansen's plans are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are they different?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you get down to it, he's just \Na coward who's afraid to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious by the way \Nhe treats those hunters!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our defeat in the New World must \Nhave shaken him to the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, all we can do is pray \Nfor the captain's recovery and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.76,0:19:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if anything should \Nhappen to the captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he's obviously going to \Ncontinue working as a hunter
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to prolong his own sorry life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it means giving up being a pirate,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather defy him and \Nchallenge the hunters to a fight
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a member of the Phoenix Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the time comes, I'll join you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I joined this band out \Nof respect for Captain Puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.18,0:20:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens to the captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can't do anything that \Nwould hurt his name!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.38,0:20:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Vigaro-san wouldn't want to \Nsee us like this from the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.30,0:20:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like everyone is \Nprepared for the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.84,0:20:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight will be a critical \Nturning point for all of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything happens to the \Ncaptain, you know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:20:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:21:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everywhere you look, there are icebergs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something feels off...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of these icebergs,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.17,0:21:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it almost feels like the ship \Nis following a path of its own...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang, talk about dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun, look ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.84,0:21:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What--?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.22,0:21:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard aport!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew, that was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was with that iceberg?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came out of nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is something weird about these icebergs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they're moving on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.43,0:21:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, those new recruits screwed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I was sure to chase our \Nprey into the usual area, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't your place to call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.13,0:21:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we may only be \Nbrothers-in-law, but we are still--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.59,0:21:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Campaccino!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.32,0:21:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you're teasing my honey again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.49,0:22:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Salchow, you didn't fail to finish \Noff that big fish, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, but, I didn't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.45,0:22:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did everything I could!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.70,0:22:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.41,0:22:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.50,0:22:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't expect me to pamper you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm so cold without you that \NI'm afraid I'll freeze, Arbell!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.22,0:22:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're so silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.46,0:22:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The party is on hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to have to personally \Nhunt down that prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The timing couldn't be better!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can work together as siblings to \Ncatchthem as our birthday present for Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.24,0:22:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait until you see \Nwhat we bring in, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.91,0:22:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Arbell!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.89,0:22:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't, Lil!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.09,0:22:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.36,0:22:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm paired with my darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.24,0:22:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.69,0:22:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A total bounty of 600 million Berries, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see their Jolly Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.04,0:22:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we celebrate early?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:22:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May our beloved Papa, Don Accino,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.72,0:23:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Accino Family's knitblood \Nrelations be blessed!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.56,0:23:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here's to our present for Papa--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.31,0:23:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the heads of the Straw Hat Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.41,0:23:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now head on out, my \Nbeloved sons and daughters!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.51,0:23:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for the hunt to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.71,0:23:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun, hard aport!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.13,0:23:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.67,0:23:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is with these waters?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.65,0:23:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It goes from one thing to the next!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.97,0:23:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like they're luring us somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.84,0:23:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.47,0:23:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard a-starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.96,0:23:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rudder's frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.67,0:23:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are Luffy and Chopper ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.30,0:23:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Dream Sinking in the New World! \NThe Disillusioned Pirate, Puzzle"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.95,0:23:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
